A-Bus - a lightweight message bus system

How to install from svn
1) Install autotools, libtool, pkg-config, build-essential
   For test framework: libgtest-dev >= 1.6.0
      and pass --enable-test to configure script
   For test FastCGI gateway: libfcgi-dev
      and pass --enable-fcgi to configure script

2) In main dir start
    a) autoreconf -i --force
    b) ./configure --prefix=/usr/local --enable-examples --enable-maintainer-mode
    c) make
    d) make install

How to build tar package:
=> Same as svn build, but skip 2.a) and maintainer-mode not necessary

Project: http://code.google.com/p/exfat/
Mailing list: http://groups.google.com/group/abus-discuss
